            <tr><td class="ts-pad" style="padding:40px 44px 44px;">
              
    
    <p style="margin:0 0 10px;font-family:'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.16em;color:#2c5bff;font-weight:600;">
      <span style="display:inline-block;width:18px;height:1px;background-color:#05dbd6;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:10px;"></span>Application update
    </p>
    <h1 class="ts-headline" style="margin:0 0 24px;font-family:'Instrument Serif', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'DejaVu Serif', serif;font-size:30px;color:#11123c;font-weight:400;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.015em;">Confirming our earlier message</h1>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#2f3941;line-height:1.7;">Hi Thabo Mokoena,</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#2f3941;line-height:1.7;">This is a written confirmation of the message shared with you in your chat: the recruitment team for the <strong>Senior Backend Engineer</strong> position at <strong>Açme & Co <Pty> Ltd</strong> has decided not to move forward with your application.</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-family:'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#2f3941;line-height:1.7;">They asked us to share the following note: &ldquo;Strong CV, but we&#39;ve gone with someone closer to the &quot;must-have&quot; stack.&rdquo;</p>
    <p style="margin:20px 0 0;padding-top:18px;border-top:1px solid #d1dce6;font-family:'Instrument Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#5a6b7a;line-height:1.65;">We appreciate the time you invested and wish you the very best in your career.</p>
  
            </td></tr>
          </table>

        </td></tr>
      </table>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <table role="presentation" width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:580px;width:100%;">
